definition: to await a decision/to be pending
to wait/to treat/to deal with/to need/going to (do sth)/about to/intending to
to set/to fix/to determine/to decide/to order

sentences.english: L′Hospital law is an important tool of obtaining undetermined type limit.

sentences.english: The unknown integration constants in the general solution can be determined by means of the boundary conditions.
sentences.chinese: 然后利用边界条件确定通解中的待定常数。

sentences.english: Every school handles wait-listed students differently.
sentences.chinese: 对待定学生的处理办法，各个院校是不一样的。

sentences.english: The method of indetermined coefficients can be applied to some other cases as well.

sentences.english: In this paper, we present the proofs of Lagrange Theory and Cauchy Theory. By this method we may determine coefficient.
